text.tspan: Women's political empowerment weighted by population
Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem. It captures the extent to which women enjoy civil liberties,
can participate in civil society, and are represented in politics. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most empowered).
Source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
